Uses for disabled buttons or not, also for checkboxes selected or not 

boolean closeIconPresent= driver.findElement(closeIcon).isDisplayed(); // returns true of element is present

boolean closeIconPresent= driver.findElement(closeIcon).isEnabled(); //if button is enabled then it will return true 

boolean closeIconPresent= driver.findElement(closeIcon).isSelected(); //return wheather checkbox is selected OR not 

element.isSelected() // Wheather a checkbox or radio button is selected or not 
element.isEnabled() // Whather checkbox or radio button is enabled state or not
element.isDisplayed // whather the checkbox or radio button is displayed or not 

if you want to deSelect the checkbox or radio button then simply we can check whather it is selected or not if it's selected then click so it will deselect 

if(ele.isSelected())
 ele.click();
